casebody.data:
Stephen Michael WEST, petitioner,
v.
Tony PARKER, Commissioner, Tennessee Department of Corrections, et al. No. 19-5561 (19A161). Supreme Court of the United States Aug. 15, 2019.

*26Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice SOTOMAYOR and by her referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
